 New World in September 1620. The Mayflower set sail from Plymouth, England, with 102 passengers, 40 of whom called themselves \"\"Saints.\"\" After two stormy months at sea, the ship reached the New World. Nearly half of the group died during their first winter due to malnutrition and the harsh New England winter.\"","url":"https://www.themayflowersociety.org/the-pilgrims/pilgrim-history","urlTitle":"The Mayflower Society - Pilgrim History","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Hughe Rychardes was born in 1556, in Kenn, Devon, England. He married Dewnes Waltham on 25 June 1576, in Kenn, Devon, England. They were the parents of at least 2 sons and 1 daughter. He died in 1628, in his hometown, at the age of 72."},"et":{"1556–1628":"1556–1628","1548–Female":"1548–Surnud","1576–1628":"1576–1628","1581–Male":"1581–Surnud","1583–Female":"1583–Surnud","1586–Female":"1586–Surnud","1588–Female":"1588–Surnud","1583":"1583","1581":"1581","25 June 1576":"25. juuni 1576","1569":"1569","1558":"1558","1556":"1556","1600":"1600","1588":"1588","1620":"1620","1587":"1587","1576":"1576","21 March 1576":"21. märts 1576","1586":"1586","1585":"1585","1628":"1628","1548":"1548","Kenn, Devon, England":"Kenn, Devon, England","England":"England"},"fi":{"1556–1628":"1556–1628","1548–Female":"1548–Kuollut","1576–1628":"1576–1628","1581–Male":"1581–Kuollut","1583–Female":"1583–Kuollut","1586–Female":"1586–Kuollut","1588–Female":"1588–Kuollut","1583":"1583","1581":"1581","25 June 1576":"25. kesäkuuta 1576","1569":"1569","1558":"1558","1556":"1556","1600":"1600","1588":"1588","1620":"1620","1587":"1587","1576":"1576","21 March 1576":"21. maaliskuuta 1576","1586":"1586","1585":"1585","1628":"1628","1548":"1548","Kenn, Devon, England":"Kenn, Devon, England","England":"England"},"fr":{"1556–1628":"1556–1628","1548–Female":"1548–Décédée","1576–1628":"1576–1628","1581–Male":"1581–Décédé","1583–Female":"1583–Décédée","1586–Female":"1586–Décédée","1588–Female":"1588–Décédée","1583":"1583","1581":"1581